WEBVTT

00:08.261 --> 00:09.401
Lord Song.

00:10.401 --> 00:12.170
(Song Ancestral Hall)

00:12.171 --> 00:13.140
Lord Song.

00:13.141 --> 00:14.650
The Duke requests your presence.

00:14.651 --> 00:16.241
The elders from both families are here.

00:16.411 --> 00:17.551
I'm not going.

00:17.851 --> 00:20.041
I don't see the need to be there.

00:20.371 --> 00:21.921
Since everything is already arranged,

00:21.941 --> 00:23.471
why put on airs and graces now?

00:23.651 --> 00:24.791
Lord Song.

00:24.941 --> 00:28.041
His Majesty has decreed.

00:28.141 --> 00:29.881
If word of this gets out,

00:30.171 --> 00:33.671
people would chastise both of you
for being ill-mannered

00:33.731 --> 00:35.281
and disregarding your family duties.

00:35.501 --> 00:37.300
Even the officials

00:37.301 --> 00:39.690
may call you disrespectful and rude.

00:39.691 --> 00:41.711
My reputation has never been pristine.

00:41.771 --> 00:42.911
I don't care.

00:43.621 --> 00:44.761
You should go.

00:46.101 --> 00:47.741
It's good for you
to see what's going on.

00:48.051 --> 00:49.180
Ms. Longevity.

00:49.181 --> 00:51.351
Even in a war, civility comes first.

00:51.451 --> 00:53.921
Besides, we'll be staying
here for a long time.

00:54.091 --> 00:55.991
We can't avoid them forever.

00:56.451 --> 00:58.711
You have never been one
to back down so easily.

00:59.051 --> 01:00.241
What's wrong with you now?

01:00.331 --> 01:01.471
Are you scared?

01:02.821 --> 01:04.241
Why would I be scared of them?

01:05.931 --> 01:07.121
But I promised you

01:07.131 --> 01:09.071
that you wouldn't have
to deal with such trouble.

01:09.931 --> 01:11.791
This is only our first day of marriage.

01:12.821 --> 01:13.961
It's fine.

01:14.211 --> 01:15.351
Come on.

02:41.481 --> 02:45.600
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

02:45.601 --> 02:48.640
=Episode 20=

02:48.641 --> 02:51.061
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

03:00.421 --> 03:02.521
You offered tea to Huisun first?

03:02.601 --> 03:04.591
You offered tea
to a dead person before us.

03:04.701 --> 03:06.361
You have no regard for rules.

03:10.261 --> 03:11.660
We didn't know that all of you

03:11.661 --> 03:13.311
have been waiting for us here.

03:13.611 --> 03:14.801
It's just that

03:15.411 --> 03:18.191
the dead must always
be remembered and honored.

03:18.451 --> 03:20.060
That's what His Majesty said

03:20.061 --> 03:21.591
during one of his hunting trips.

03:21.721 --> 03:23.290
What a glib tongue.

03:23.291 --> 03:24.410
(Wife of the Eldest Uncle)

03:24.411 --> 03:25.841
Even the tea has turned cold.

03:26.101 --> 03:29.010
Is this how you act
right after you married into our family?

03:29.011 --> 03:31.711
Yes, the tea has gone cold.

03:31.921 --> 03:32.991
You should brew

03:33.001 --> 03:34.980
(Wife of the Third Uncle)
a new pot of tea for us.

03:34.981 --> 03:36.121
Come on.

03:40.541 --> 03:42.801
Eldest Uncle, Third Uncle,
have you forgotten

03:42.931 --> 03:46.151
what happened here?

03:50.311 --> 03:52.130
Yizhi Hall detached itself
from this residence

03:52.131 --> 03:54.241
soon after my mother passed away.

03:54.511 --> 03:57.071
As the saying goes, "when
everyone has left, the tea turns cold."

03:57.891 --> 03:59.431
That's why the tea is already cold.

03:59.821 --> 04:01.130
Do not forget

04:01.131 --> 04:03.531
that you are the future Duke of Ying!

04:08.411 --> 04:09.561
You are right, Father-in-law.

04:10.361 --> 04:12.541
Now that I am married to Lord Song,

04:13.161 --> 04:14.711
that makes me the future duke's wife.

04:27.431 --> 04:28.791
Father-in-law, drink some tea.

05:01.481 --> 05:03.131
(General)
This is for you, Sister-in-law.

05:03.411 --> 05:05.881
My brother used to play chess with me
whenever he returned.

05:05.981 --> 05:08.081
We may not play regularly anymore,

05:08.291 --> 05:11.281
but you're here to keep him company.

05:12.411 --> 05:13.551
Thank you, Han.

05:15.461 --> 05:17.471
It's not like I'd have
your brother all to myself.

05:17.481 --> 05:19.420
Now that you have
a sister-in-law to dote on you,

05:19.421 --> 05:20.841
you should visit us more often.

05:21.781 --> 05:22.640
See?

05:22.641 --> 05:24.651
Han is such a sensible child.

05:25.021 --> 05:27.370
Actually, we have prepared gifts
for our new niece-in-law.

05:27.371 --> 05:29.321
All that talking
made us forget about it.

05:29.371 --> 05:30.511
Bring the gifts.

05:31.371 --> 05:32.671
Thank you for the gifts.

05:33.611 --> 05:34.960
I guess there's a lot I need

05:34.961 --> 05:36.441
to learn from you as a newly wed.

05:37.411 --> 05:39.121
Since I am now part of this family,

05:39.361 --> 05:41.111
I shall humbly learn from you.

05:41.841 --> 05:43.371
It's not that much.

05:43.901 --> 05:45.410
Now that Yantang is married,

05:45.411 --> 05:48.001
our family has decided to do our part

05:48.231 --> 05:50.591
and renovate Yizhi Hall

05:50.841 --> 05:52.351
as a token of our affection.

05:54.061 --> 05:55.621
That's a wonderful idea.

05:55.701 --> 05:58.361
Once Zhao deposits her dowry
into the residence's treasury,

05:58.701 --> 06:01.321
you may proceed with the renovations.

06:02.501 --> 06:04.081
This farcical ceremony

06:04.591 --> 06:06.031
and your sweet promises

06:06.361 --> 06:07.340
are just a ruse

06:07.341 --> 06:09.231
to confiscate Zhao's dowry.

06:09.631 --> 06:12.531
By tradition, the eldest daughter-in-law
is the mistress of the household.

06:13.021 --> 06:16.501
Eldest Aunt, instead of handing over
the tokens and keys to the treasury,

06:16.851 --> 06:19.691
you keep eyeing on my wife's money.

06:21.701 --> 06:22.660
Yantang.

06:22.661 --> 06:24.321
That's not true.

06:24.461 --> 06:26.780
Even though we've separated
from the main residence

06:26.781 --> 06:28.231
after your mother died,

06:28.371 --> 06:31.130
your eldest aunt is still responsible

06:31.131 --> 06:32.990
for managing the finances

06:32.991 --> 06:35.801
and daily operations of the household.

06:36.021 --> 06:38.460
Your wife has just
married into our family.

06:38.461 --> 06:43.020
Someone has to guide and teach her.

06:43.021 --> 06:44.070
That's not necessary.

06:44.071 --> 06:46.141
My wife has already calculated

06:47.031 --> 06:49.471
and declared all her assets
in front of His Majesty.

06:50.021 --> 06:53.451
Even the Ministry of Revenue
has adopted her calculation formulas.

06:53.851 --> 06:55.421
I wasn't so calculative in the past,

06:55.851 --> 06:57.681
but since you are so particular
about money,

06:58.021 --> 07:01.321
we should separate
the treasury accounts too.

07:01.411 --> 07:03.231
What are you saying?

07:03.251 --> 07:06.321
The Emperor has always advised us
to maintain harmony in the family.

07:06.371 --> 07:09.081
It's improper for you to defy.

07:09.251 --> 07:11.580
Besides, running the household

07:11.581 --> 07:13.551
is no easy task.

07:13.581 --> 07:16.410
There are dozens of issues that
need to be settled every day.

07:16.411 --> 07:18.031
It's normal to stay up late.

07:18.341 --> 07:19.841
- Third Aunt...
- Third Aunt,

07:19.851 --> 07:22.151
those are exactly our biggest concerns.

07:22.461 --> 07:24.140
Money is simply superficial.

07:24.141 --> 07:26.151
Family harmony matters the most.

07:26.661 --> 07:28.641
Since all of you care about me,

07:28.851 --> 07:30.050
I shall let Eldest Aunt

07:30.051 --> 07:32.001
manage my dowry.

07:34.491 --> 07:35.340
Su Lan.

07:35.341 --> 07:36.671
Call Mr. Chen here.

07:36.701 --> 07:37.560
Yes.

07:37.561 --> 07:39.741
I knew my daughter-in-law
would be sensible.

07:39.851 --> 07:42.201
Your elder is willing
to go all out to help you.

07:42.551 --> 07:45.121
You must be grateful.

07:45.901 --> 07:47.081
You are right, Father-in-law.

07:55.141 --> 07:56.281
This...

07:59.781 --> 08:01.031
I thought you lost

08:01.051 --> 08:03.031
all your money in Futing?

08:03.811 --> 08:04.951
Yes.

08:05.061 --> 08:06.841
However, that was not my only asset.

08:06.931 --> 08:08.591
My other ventures
have been successful.

08:08.701 --> 08:10.441
The Miaos' potato
business has taken off.

08:10.461 --> 08:12.081
I funded 80% of their starting capital.

08:12.221 --> 08:13.381
Young Lady.

08:13.581 --> 08:15.140
I did a rough calculation.

08:15.141 --> 08:16.641
There's about 70,000 taels here.

08:16.681 --> 08:18.540
- Zhao has a keen eye for business.
- This...

08:18.541 --> 08:20.711
This is the dividend
she earned this year.

08:20.781 --> 08:23.711
You mean, 70,000 taels
is just the dividend?

08:26.081 --> 08:27.020
Just two chests of these

08:27.021 --> 08:29.841
is worth ten years' of food
expenses in the residence.

08:30.291 --> 08:31.580
Don't act like an ignorant fool.

08:31.581 --> 08:32.961
She might laugh at you.

08:34.891 --> 08:36.610
I was planning to deposit my dowry

08:36.611 --> 08:37.650
and the dividend here

08:37.651 --> 08:39.241
into the residence's treasury

08:39.301 --> 08:40.730
to share the elders' burden

08:40.731 --> 08:42.551
by managing the residence's accounts.

08:43.011 --> 08:46.071
By then, our wealth is expected
to grow by 20% every year.

08:46.461 --> 08:49.401
Our real estate, trading,
and agricultural ventures

08:49.611 --> 08:52.151
can generate at least
70,000 to 80,000 taels in profit.

08:52.251 --> 08:55.001
Now that Eldest Aunt
will manage everything,

08:55.131 --> 08:57.601
I'm sure you will earn more than I do.

08:59.301 --> 09:01.700
70,000 to 80,000 taels a year?

09:01.701 --> 09:03.071
How could I?

09:03.421 --> 09:04.641
Yes, yes.

09:04.711 --> 09:06.140
My dowry also includes

09:06.141 --> 09:07.881
some farming lands and shops

09:08.281 --> 09:10.150
that I have co-invested with other

09:10.151 --> 09:11.000
aristocratic ladies.

09:11.001 --> 09:13.801
If our profits were to fall,

09:13.851 --> 09:16.191
I'm afraid they'd stop working with us.

09:16.491 --> 09:17.631
After all, it's important

09:17.741 --> 09:19.601
to maintain business credibility.

09:19.651 --> 09:21.080
Once you lose it,

09:21.081 --> 09:22.950
it's hard to maintain
business connections,

09:22.951 --> 09:25.361
and you might even
offend other stakeholders.

09:26.371 --> 09:27.620
Everyone in the capital knows

09:27.621 --> 09:29.361
(Eldest Daughter-In-Law)
that you're a skilled businesswoman.

09:29.471 --> 09:31.661
My mother-in-law spends all her time
managing the household.

09:31.671 --> 09:32.980
It's not even worth mentioning

09:32.981 --> 09:34.601
compared to your business ventures.

09:34.651 --> 09:36.250
I guess it's better

09:36.251 --> 09:37.980
that we keep our accounts separate

09:37.981 --> 09:39.370
so that we don't end up arguing

09:39.371 --> 09:41.431
over money matters.

09:42.581 --> 09:44.031
As a man,

09:44.731 --> 09:48.031
it is pathetic to eye
on his wife's dowry.

09:48.251 --> 09:49.391
Miss Miao,

09:49.491 --> 09:51.031
take the money back

09:51.181 --> 09:53.361
so that we don't
attract unwanted gossip.

09:53.731 --> 09:57.130
Sure, I'll continue managing
Zhao's business on her behalf.

09:57.131 --> 09:58.271
Take them back.

09:58.851 --> 10:00.401
- No...
- This is...

10:01.421 --> 10:02.561
Zhao.

10:02.611 --> 10:04.220
Mind telling me

10:04.221 --> 10:05.770
how you earned so much money?

10:05.771 --> 10:07.180
I didn't expect

10:07.181 --> 10:09.071
that we have such
a capable niece-in-law.

10:09.421 --> 10:11.700
Yichun, why don't we let her

10:11.701 --> 10:13.010
manage the residence's

10:13.011 --> 10:14.890
private assets as well?

10:14.891 --> 10:16.490
She's family, after all.

10:16.491 --> 10:17.530
We can trust her, right?

10:17.531 --> 10:19.401
Yes, that's a great idea.

10:21.701 --> 10:22.841
If that's what you wish,

10:22.851 --> 10:24.311
I wouldn't say no,

10:24.851 --> 10:28.521
but if my father-in-law doesn't agree,

10:28.701 --> 10:32.031
I wouldn't defy him.

10:32.301 --> 10:33.220
Yichun.

10:33.221 --> 10:34.340
You...

10:34.341 --> 10:35.481
Yichun.

10:39.061 --> 10:40.641
I'm keeping my hands off this.

10:41.101 --> 10:42.241
Wait.

10:42.651 --> 10:43.831
- Yichun.
- Yichun.

10:44.011 --> 10:46.401
- Yichun.
- Yichun, you can't just leave.

10:46.461 --> 10:47.530
Zhao.

10:47.531 --> 10:48.580
Can you also

10:48.581 --> 10:50.460
reserve a spot for us

10:50.461 --> 10:52.281
- in your business ventures too?
- Yes, Zhao.

10:52.351 --> 10:53.801
We have some savings.

10:53.811 --> 10:55.561
- We can pass them to you...
- I thought she

10:55.571 --> 10:57.551
was good at observing palace politics,

10:57.941 --> 10:59.551
but I didn't know she's also good

10:59.981 --> 11:01.241
at managing household affairs.

11:01.301 --> 11:04.281
I know you want to protect her,

11:04.611 --> 11:07.071
but the deaths of
the Duke of Ding and Mrs Jiang

11:07.301 --> 11:09.031
are connected.

11:09.821 --> 11:11.401
In this large residence,

11:11.981 --> 11:14.401
we can only start investigating
through money allocations

11:14.421 --> 11:16.721
and what the servants say and do.

11:16.821 --> 11:19.601
Young Lady is trying to gain power here

11:19.611 --> 11:21.401
so that she could help you

11:21.701 --> 11:23.460
win the favor of the household.

11:23.461 --> 11:26.710
By then, we will get to access
the matching tokens.

11:26.711 --> 11:27.901
That's right.

11:29.201 --> 11:30.460
(Meritorious Service)
Yichun.

11:30.461 --> 11:32.820
You can't just stay out of this.

11:32.821 --> 11:34.850
We're talking about
70,000 to 80,000 taels.

11:34.851 --> 11:38.241
As they say, money is king.

11:38.701 --> 11:39.540
Exactly.

11:39.541 --> 11:40.591
We don't have to be scared

11:40.601 --> 11:42.610
since the matching tokens
are still in our hands.

11:42.611 --> 11:43.831
That's right.

11:46.251 --> 11:48.121
Have I not treated you well?

11:48.851 --> 11:50.371
She's only been here for a day,

11:50.381 --> 11:52.370
and yet she's already got you
all under her thumb?

11:52.371 --> 11:53.511
No...

11:53.611 --> 11:55.601
You're a disgrace to our ancestors!

11:56.371 --> 11:58.031
What a stubborn man.

11:59.371 --> 12:00.511
Come on.

12:01.101 --> 12:02.241
Yichun.

12:02.301 --> 12:04.031
This is about money.

12:04.771 --> 12:06.420
Stop wasting your
breath on him, Brother.

12:06.421 --> 12:07.601
Come out!

12:15.061 --> 12:16.201
Your Grace.

12:20.491 --> 12:21.951
Don't worry.

12:21.981 --> 12:23.671
Everyone in the residence
is loyal to you.

12:23.731 --> 12:24.940
She's just a newcomer.

12:24.941 --> 12:26.610
The servants wouldn't listen to her.

12:26.611 --> 12:28.951
She'd soon realize
how difficult it is to survive here.

12:29.491 --> 12:31.721
I underestimated Dou Zhao.

12:32.251 --> 12:34.100
To think a young lass like her

12:34.101 --> 12:35.601
could be so sly.

12:36.771 --> 12:39.490
Perhaps I made a mistake

12:39.491 --> 12:41.751
and infuriated that defiant son of mine?

12:42.201 --> 12:43.420
Everyone in the capital knows

12:43.421 --> 12:45.521
that my father and I
have separated our households.

12:45.531 --> 12:47.010
As for my uncles, aunts

12:47.011 --> 12:48.370
and their daughter-in-law,

12:48.371 --> 12:50.220
you don't have to
worry about their assets.

12:50.221 --> 12:52.191
Better yet, you don't have
to interact with them,

12:52.551 --> 12:54.121
or else you might fall sick from anger.

12:54.821 --> 12:55.770
I approached them

12:55.771 --> 12:57.551
not to let them infuriate me.

12:57.571 --> 13:00.051
Your father doesn't want me
to manage the residence's treasury

13:00.101 --> 13:02.601
and tries to convince
his brothers to stop me.

13:02.941 --> 13:05.481
However, they've never been of one mind.

13:05.851 --> 13:07.650
Your uncles are money-hungry.

13:07.651 --> 13:09.471
Your eldest aunt
isn't as strong as she looks.

13:09.481 --> 13:11.521
Your third aunt is an easy read.

13:12.201 --> 13:14.300
They may seem to follow
your father's arrangements,

13:14.301 --> 13:16.281
but they all have their own minds.

13:16.511 --> 13:18.831
Only your eldest uncle's
daughter-in-law is clever enough

13:19.181 --> 13:22.110
to know that if she gets caught between you
and your father,

13:22.111 --> 13:23.521
the deal would be off.

13:23.531 --> 13:25.001
She may be our breakthrough point.

13:31.771 --> 13:32.911
What's wrong?

13:34.221 --> 13:37.361
You know them well
though you've only met them once.

13:37.851 --> 13:41.121
How could my wife be so clever?

13:42.421 --> 13:45.281
Back when I saved Wu Shan in the manor,

13:45.301 --> 13:47.911
you also immediately recognized
the hidden dynamics in my family.

13:48.781 --> 13:50.220
In fact, you're better at identifying

13:50.221 --> 13:52.151
the subtle expressions
on people's faces.

13:55.651 --> 13:57.770
If the Duke of Ying's Residence

13:57.771 --> 13:59.220
tries to do anything funny,

13:59.221 --> 14:01.370
get Mr. Chen to find me
at the Imperial Guards.

14:01.371 --> 14:02.511
Don't carry the burden alone.

14:03.371 --> 14:06.071
You just called me
a strategist last night,

14:06.221 --> 14:07.521
and now you don't trust me?

14:09.611 --> 14:10.911
It's not that.

14:11.301 --> 14:12.441
I'm just worried.

14:14.011 --> 14:15.100
By the way,

14:15.101 --> 14:17.401
let me give you something as protection.

14:19.941 --> 14:21.401
This is my first time.

14:22.011 --> 14:23.151
It's fine.

14:23.611 --> 14:24.761
Stay calm.

14:26.061 --> 14:27.201
Look at your target.

14:27.651 --> 14:28.791
Aim.

14:37.651 --> 14:39.431
This is even louder than the fireworks.

14:39.651 --> 14:41.881
- Careful, it's hot.
- You didn't even blink.

14:43.101 --> 14:45.031
It's normal to be scared
on your first try.

14:51.011 --> 14:53.481
The more scared you are,
the calmer you need to be.

14:53.701 --> 14:54.841
Stay calm.

14:57.701 --> 14:58.841
Relax.

14:59.181 --> 15:00.361
I'm beside you.

15:15.061 --> 15:16.201
I missed.

15:16.851 --> 15:18.121
You're already doing a good job.

15:24.371 --> 15:26.721
If you can hit the wind chimes today,

15:26.911 --> 15:28.311
you'd pass your first entrance test.

15:28.461 --> 15:29.601
Try it.

15:30.731 --> 15:32.071
I'm going to freshen up.

15:48.731 --> 15:49.871
I hit it!

15:49.941 --> 15:51.151
I hit it!

15:51.641 --> 15:52.781
My dear.

15:53.281 --> 15:54.601
You have talent.

15:57.221 --> 15:58.361
What happened to your hand?

15:58.891 --> 16:00.031
Show me.

16:01.251 --> 16:02.391
Why is it bleeding again?

16:02.491 --> 16:03.490
It's fine.

16:03.491 --> 16:04.631
It's nothing.

16:11.491 --> 16:12.631
Yantang.

16:14.061 --> 16:16.601
I said I can bathe by myself.

16:17.941 --> 16:19.601
Your hand is still injured.

16:19.611 --> 16:21.741
Before it heals, you need
to keep it away from water.

16:22.421 --> 16:23.530
Allow me.

16:23.531 --> 16:24.671
It's fine.

16:25.491 --> 16:26.671
I can manage myself.

16:29.981 --> 16:31.401
Allow me.

16:31.971 --> 16:34.261
If I can't take care of you
when you're injured,

16:34.371 --> 16:36.071
how could I call myself your wife?

16:48.821 --> 16:52.761
I didn't expect that
the mighty General Song

16:52.941 --> 16:54.521
can feel shy sometimes.

17:03.201 --> 17:06.521
♪Riding across the desolate battlefield in the wind♪

17:06.931 --> 17:10.091
♪The turbulence unfolding one after another♪

17:11.181 --> 17:13.820
♪The lingering uncertainty has yet been resolved♪

17:13.821 --> 17:18.290
♪I gaze at you, and all is calm♪

17:18.291 --> 17:21.380
♪The world is vast and turbulent♪

17:21.381 --> 17:23.311
When I said I could manage,

17:23.531 --> 17:24.721
I wasn't being shy.

17:25.571 --> 17:26.800
I didn't want to scare you.

17:26.801 --> 17:30.841
♪When the time comes,
all pride will be laid down♪

17:32.531 --> 17:34.530
Back at Zhaowen Bookstore,

17:34.531 --> 17:37.871
after Mr. Chen bandaged
your wounds, he said

17:38.221 --> 17:40.001
that your back is covered in scars.

17:41.181 --> 17:44.071
I see them now.

17:45.601 --> 17:49.720
♪Ferrying me to the other side♪

17:49.721 --> 17:53.771
♪You're my light of redemption
amid the darkness♪

17:54.151 --> 17:57.780
♪You're my saving grace♪

17:57.781 --> 17:59.851
♪Warming my heart♪

18:02.051 --> 18:04.311
Ms. Longevity, I'm sorry.

18:05.091 --> 18:06.521
You got these scars from defending

18:07.051 --> 18:09.551
our nation and people.

18:10.011 --> 18:13.391
In fact, you injured your shoulder
to protect me.

18:13.771 --> 18:15.311
There's nothing to apologize for.

18:19.421 --> 18:20.561
Yantang.

18:21.941 --> 18:23.681
When two people live together,

18:24.291 --> 18:25.431
the most important thing

18:25.981 --> 18:28.180
is to make each other feel
more comfortable

18:28.181 --> 18:29.351
and free.

18:32.981 --> 18:34.281
In the future,

18:34.901 --> 18:36.681
no matter what happens,

18:37.181 --> 18:39.071
we need to be honest with each other

18:39.291 --> 18:40.551
and face everything together,

18:40.941 --> 18:42.081
won't we?

18:43.531 --> 18:45.791
Sure, I promise you.

19:07.601 --> 19:11.741
(Reinvigorating Spring)

19:12.661 --> 19:13.801
Your Lordship.

19:16.491 --> 19:17.631
You're here, Ming.

19:18.011 --> 19:19.391
You're hiding something from me?

19:19.771 --> 19:21.001
I'll see it anyway.

19:21.051 --> 19:22.191
Let me look.

19:22.381 --> 19:23.240
Ming.

19:23.241 --> 19:25.351
You'll get to see it
when I finish drawing.

19:26.091 --> 19:27.871
No, I want to see it now.

19:28.051 --> 19:29.191
Ming.

19:29.331 --> 19:30.591
This is a secret.

19:32.731 --> 19:33.871
Fine.

19:34.701 --> 19:36.071
Have some fruits, Your Lordship.

19:39.981 --> 19:41.121
Let me see!

19:41.671 --> 19:42.900
Why are you keeping it from me?

19:42.901 --> 19:44.481
- I'm not showing you.
- Let me see!

19:44.731 --> 19:46.551
Your Lordship, come on.

19:52.531 --> 19:54.591
Ming, I'll show you when it's done.

20:00.331 --> 20:01.961
Ming, you look so pretty today.

20:12.811 --> 20:14.441
Your Lordship, Your Ladyship.

20:14.461 --> 20:16.920
The Eight Treasure soup
for Madam Wei is ready.

20:16.921 --> 20:18.191
Time to greet her.

20:19.381 --> 20:20.630
Greet her?

20:20.631 --> 20:22.071
All we do is greeting those people.

20:22.381 --> 20:23.521
How annoying.

20:24.461 --> 20:25.530
Fine, you may leave now.

20:25.531 --> 20:26.671
Yes, Your Lordship.

20:28.621 --> 20:29.831
I'm going, then.

20:31.331 --> 20:32.591
Thank you, Ming.

20:35.221 --> 20:36.361
Go.

20:40.591 --> 20:42.081
How dare you talk back?

20:42.491 --> 20:43.631
What happened?

20:43.661 --> 20:45.201
Did Nanny Zhou do anything wrong?

20:45.981 --> 20:48.010
She was trying to order you around,

20:48.011 --> 20:49.570
and all I did was to rebuke her.

20:49.571 --> 20:51.311
You're serving the young duke's wife,

20:51.491 --> 20:53.330
and I'm serving the senior duke's wife.

20:53.331 --> 20:56.991
Rebuking me is an act of disrespect
towards your mistress's sister-in-law.

20:57.621 --> 20:59.250
Make sure you remember that

20:59.251 --> 21:02.631
on behalf of your mistress.

21:07.861 --> 21:09.001
Your Ladyship.

21:09.011 --> 21:10.241
- Nanny.
- Your Ladyship.

21:11.051 --> 21:12.281
Ming.

21:14.701 --> 21:16.631
Serve the soup now.

21:22.091 --> 21:23.391
Hurry up.

21:43.221 --> 21:44.391
Your Ladyship.

21:44.571 --> 21:49.111
You have to kneel and lift the bowl
over your head to show your respect.

21:54.051 --> 21:55.871
I prepared the rehmannia root

21:55.941 --> 21:58.241
in the soup all by myself.

21:58.421 --> 22:00.161
I heard this soup is beneficial

22:00.181 --> 22:02.351
for your constitution.

22:02.661 --> 22:04.220
Since this is the Duke's residence,

22:04.221 --> 22:06.351
we're very particular
about rules and decorum.

22:06.811 --> 22:10.551
From helping your mother-in-law
get dressed in the morning,

22:10.571 --> 22:13.791
to preparing your
mother-in-law's bed at night,

22:13.861 --> 22:17.241
these are your duties
as a daughter-in-law.

22:18.571 --> 22:21.391
Make sure you learn
and follow all these rules

22:22.091 --> 22:23.631
in the days to come.

22:25.571 --> 22:28.521
Your sister is already contributing
her wealth and power

22:28.571 --> 22:31.810
towards the Duke of Ying's Residence.

22:31.811 --> 22:32.951
And you?

22:33.331 --> 22:35.180
Do you even know

22:35.181 --> 22:37.050
how much money we have,

22:37.051 --> 22:38.591
and how long it'll last?

22:39.531 --> 22:41.111
The current deficit

22:41.251 --> 22:45.961
is caused by the grand funeral
held years ago

22:46.331 --> 22:48.160
when the previous duke and duchess died.

22:48.161 --> 22:52.020
You must have heard
how much Dou Zhao's dowry

22:52.021 --> 22:53.831
and personal assets are.

22:55.071 --> 22:56.881
We took you in,

22:57.191 --> 22:59.641
yet you're not showing any gratitude.

22:59.741 --> 23:03.571
All you're doing now is keeping
my silly brother happy.

23:04.011 --> 23:06.241
Have you thought about

23:06.291 --> 23:07.721
the residence's future?

23:10.281 --> 23:14.101
What happened to the benefits
your mother promised us?

23:16.831 --> 23:18.021
What are you doing?

23:20.801 --> 23:22.061
Ming, come on.

23:22.121 --> 23:23.261
Get up.

23:24.441 --> 23:25.581
Are you fine?

23:25.801 --> 23:27.101
What happened to your hands?

23:29.041 --> 23:31.181
As your sister, it's normal for me

23:31.281 --> 23:32.701
to teach your wife about decorum.

23:32.861 --> 23:34.101
This has nothing to do with you.

23:34.681 --> 23:36.101
This is my residence,

23:36.271 --> 23:37.581
not yours.

23:38.131 --> 23:39.661
Of course this is my business.

23:40.001 --> 23:41.541
If it's about money,

23:41.831 --> 23:43.661
I can sell my paintings
and calligraphy works.

23:43.761 --> 23:46.170
I know you're jealous
of Dou Zhao's dowry,

23:46.171 --> 23:47.040
but you can't vent out

23:47.041 --> 23:48.520
on Ming.

23:48.521 --> 23:49.701
What did you say?

23:50.401 --> 23:52.770
I've paid so much for you
over the years,

23:52.771 --> 23:54.281
and you've been taking it for granted.

23:54.481 --> 23:56.920
Now, all I'm asking
is that she contribute some money

23:56.921 --> 23:58.421
to help the residence,

23:58.681 --> 24:00.461
and you're chastising me?

24:00.621 --> 24:01.680
The heavens must be blind.

24:01.681 --> 24:02.920
They should have sent

24:02.921 --> 24:05.080
a bolt of lightning to strike you!

24:05.081 --> 24:06.541
Sister-in-law.

24:06.881 --> 24:07.951
I was wrong.

24:07.961 --> 24:10.631
I shouldn't have started this argument
between you and my husband.

24:10.641 --> 24:11.741
As for your request,

24:12.041 --> 24:14.421
I will ask my mother when I return home.

24:17.961 --> 24:19.040
Slow and steady does it.

24:19.041 --> 24:20.341
Be careful.

24:22.001 --> 24:23.141
Put them here.

24:28.121 --> 24:29.581
So many gifts.

24:29.881 --> 24:31.781
This must be a first in the Capital.

24:42.281 --> 24:45.061
I hope you'll enjoy
the gifts I prepared.

24:45.121 --> 24:46.461
Let's talk inside.

24:46.481 --> 24:47.621
This way.

24:58.561 --> 25:00.941
You're trying to embarrass my daughter.

25:02.281 --> 25:05.301
Still, if you weren't
as rich as you are now,

25:05.601 --> 25:08.341
I'm sure Song Mo
wouldn't treat you so well.

25:09.161 --> 25:13.221
My daughter Ming and the Duke of Jining
are happily in love.

25:13.481 --> 25:15.621
They don't need
these material possessions.

25:16.361 --> 25:17.501
You are

25:17.681 --> 25:20.341
just a pitiful girl.

25:21.441 --> 25:23.240
Hearing these words from your mouth

25:23.241 --> 25:24.701
is actually surprising.

25:25.441 --> 25:26.981
Money is hard-earned,

25:27.121 --> 25:29.101
but love fades easily.

25:29.801 --> 25:30.920
This is what

25:30.921 --> 25:33.741
I learned from you years ago.

25:41.121 --> 25:42.080
Seventh Madam.

25:42.081 --> 25:44.141
The Duchess of Jining is back.

25:46.441 --> 25:49.581
Your looks haven't changed
over the years, Mother.

25:49.841 --> 25:52.440
We don't look like
mother and daughter now.

25:52.441 --> 25:53.941
Instead, we look like sisters.

25:54.041 --> 25:55.181
Exactly.

25:55.601 --> 25:57.280
I feel so relieved

25:57.281 --> 25:58.960
now that you're no longer here,

25:58.961 --> 26:01.421
so I look younger naturally.

26:03.321 --> 26:04.541
On the contrary,

26:05.401 --> 26:07.261
it's only been a while
since you got married,

26:07.641 --> 26:09.880
and you've lost so much weight.

26:09.881 --> 26:12.661
Has Wei Tingzhen been abusing you?

26:13.121 --> 26:14.340
Is this how the Duchess of Jing

26:14.341 --> 26:15.941
behaves as a sister-in-law?

26:16.681 --> 26:17.821
Someday,

26:17.901 --> 26:19.741
I'll settle these scores with her.

26:20.841 --> 26:21.920
Mother.

26:21.921 --> 26:23.720
The Duke is protective of me.

26:23.721 --> 26:25.301
He treats me very well.

26:25.841 --> 26:27.141
As if.

26:27.161 --> 26:29.301
What gifts did he bring

26:29.401 --> 26:30.840
the last time he came?

26:30.841 --> 26:32.301
Just look at your sister today.

26:33.001 --> 26:35.221
The Duke and I don't care about that.

26:36.641 --> 26:39.941
But your residence needs to maintain
a certain standard of living.

26:40.561 --> 26:41.880
Even if he doesn't care,

26:41.881 --> 26:43.541
his sister won't just sit by and watch.

26:44.841 --> 26:45.981
Mother.

26:46.161 --> 26:47.861
You don't have to worry about me.

26:48.001 --> 26:50.400
She's nice to me, too.

26:50.401 --> 26:51.541
That's enough.

26:51.561 --> 26:52.981
Don't try to fool me.

26:53.601 --> 26:55.640
You think I don't know

26:55.641 --> 26:57.261
what kind of person Wei Tingzhen is?

26:57.761 --> 26:58.720
If she knows

26:58.721 --> 27:00.861
how much Dou Zhao's dowry is worth,

27:01.121 --> 27:03.710
she'd make your life hellish

27:03.711 --> 27:04.941
in the Duke's residence.

27:05.201 --> 27:08.221
You insisted on marrying him,

27:08.841 --> 27:11.541
and now you can't even tell me
how much you're suffering there.

27:12.201 --> 27:14.061
You useless girl.

27:15.721 --> 27:17.581
I know everyone is comparing

27:17.961 --> 27:20.621
my sister's dowry and mine,

27:20.961 --> 27:23.261
but why are you also
doing this to me, Mother?

27:23.961 --> 27:26.000
What else can I say?

27:26.001 --> 27:26.871
Ever since I was born,

27:26.881 --> 27:29.021
everything I do is a mistake
in your eyes.

27:29.761 --> 27:30.901
If that's the case,

27:30.961 --> 27:32.621
I shall not linger around and annoy you.

27:36.321 --> 27:37.461
Your Ladyship...

27:37.561 --> 27:39.000
Look at her.

27:39.001 --> 27:40.560
She's unhappy about her in-laws,

27:40.561 --> 27:42.080
and she's bickering with me?

27:42.081 --> 27:43.040
Look at her behavior.

27:43.041 --> 27:44.381
She's just like her father.

27:44.801 --> 27:45.760
Madam.

27:45.761 --> 27:46.840
You don't know

27:46.841 --> 27:48.280
how much Ming is suffering

27:48.281 --> 27:49.781
over there.

28:01.001 --> 28:02.141
Ming.

28:05.081 --> 28:06.221
What happened?

28:14.161 --> 28:15.301
Why are you crying?

28:17.321 --> 28:18.970
Ming must be missing home

28:18.971 --> 28:20.301
since she just got married.

28:23.411 --> 28:25.221
Why don't we let them chat

28:25.281 --> 28:27.341
while we enjoy a drink?

28:41.101 --> 28:43.751
After getting married, I realized

28:44.161 --> 28:47.301
that your advice was true.

28:47.521 --> 28:49.141
The Duke's residence

28:49.321 --> 28:51.461
is not as wonderful as outsiders think.

28:52.161 --> 28:55.221
They insist on putting up appearances
even when they're broke inside.

28:55.961 --> 28:57.261
I don't have the capabilities

28:57.761 --> 28:59.221
to cover their deficits

28:59.321 --> 29:01.141
or maintain their facade.

29:02.161 --> 29:04.341
Let's not talk about the past.

29:04.621 --> 29:07.421
You should focus on the future.

29:08.681 --> 29:10.480
The higher a family's status,

29:10.481 --> 29:13.021
the bigger their deficits.

29:13.121 --> 29:14.541
Don't blame yourself.

29:17.121 --> 29:18.320
My dowry is nothing

29:18.321 --> 29:20.141
compared to the debts

29:20.201 --> 29:21.981
they have accrued.

29:22.401 --> 29:25.560
How can I, a domestic lady,

29:25.561 --> 29:27.261
get the money to pay their debts?

29:29.681 --> 29:32.440
While domestic life can seem trivial,

29:32.441 --> 29:34.461
there are many things
to pay attention to.

29:34.471 --> 29:36.461
For example, the rice
from Liaodong may be softer,

29:36.471 --> 29:37.781
but it costs 900 wen per dan.

29:37.961 --> 29:40.821
Meanwhile, rice from Jiangnan is firmer,
and it only costs 700 wen.

29:40.881 --> 29:43.971
So, when you're cooking rice or congee,
for every two parts of Liaodong rice,

29:44.001 --> 29:45.271
mix in one part of Jiangnan rice,

29:45.281 --> 29:46.861
and it'll taste just as good.

29:47.241 --> 29:48.320
You can save

29:48.321 --> 29:50.381
up to 500 to 600 taels a year.

29:50.681 --> 29:52.440
You can deposit half of it in the bank

29:52.441 --> 29:54.021
and invest the rest in the tea trade

29:54.041 --> 29:55.621
to earn thousands of taels a year.

29:55.721 --> 29:57.101
That's an amazing idea.

29:57.801 --> 30:00.681
Sister, you must be the goddess
of wealth in your past life.

30:02.121 --> 30:03.120
Besides,

30:03.121 --> 30:05.301
you need to manage
your residence's assets.

30:05.681 --> 30:09.440
If you have any taverns or shops
that haven't been making profits,

30:09.441 --> 30:10.721
you should sell them off

30:10.731 --> 30:13.451
and reinvest the money in booming trades
like fragrances and apparel.

30:13.461 --> 30:14.141
No need.

30:16.001 --> 30:17.141
Ming.

30:28.121 --> 30:30.461
My father and I will support Ming,

30:30.601 --> 30:33.141
so she doesn't have to
learn your miserly ways.

30:33.241 --> 30:34.381
I will make sure

30:34.401 --> 30:36.541
that Ming doesn't live in poverty.

30:37.421 --> 30:38.650
I'll get my father

30:38.651 --> 30:42.160
to assign a position for her husband.

30:42.161 --> 30:43.901
Once the Duke's career takes off,

30:44.041 --> 30:46.160
they won't have to worry over

30:46.161 --> 30:47.421
such material concerns.

30:48.741 --> 30:49.881
Come on.

31:01.761 --> 31:02.901
Mother.

31:03.161 --> 31:05.341
Did you really mean that?

31:05.441 --> 31:07.821
But, Grandfather has always been fair,

31:07.841 --> 31:09.261
and he despises nepotism.

31:09.721 --> 31:10.880
Why would he...

31:10.881 --> 31:12.021
You know,

31:13.011 --> 31:14.621
when you have children,

31:15.401 --> 31:17.701
you can't live for yourself.

31:18.561 --> 31:20.461
Back when my father was demoted,

31:20.751 --> 31:23.781
I had to cast my pride aside
and sell porridge to earn a living.

31:24.881 --> 31:26.421
Now, I'll do this again

31:27.241 --> 31:29.181
for your sake.

31:29.441 --> 31:31.461
I'll beg my father to make an exception.

31:32.841 --> 31:34.680
(One hundred taels)

31:34.681 --> 31:36.021
Take these.

31:41.081 --> 31:42.080
Mother.

31:42.081 --> 31:43.621
I can't take these.

31:43.641 --> 31:45.461
I know that you're

31:45.481 --> 31:47.360
facing a difficult time too.

31:47.361 --> 31:49.301
How did you get so much money?

31:51.161 --> 31:52.901
I may be useless,

31:53.321 --> 31:55.141
but I cannot be a bad daughter.

31:59.681 --> 32:01.880
Illegal moneylending is a major crime.

32:01.881 --> 32:03.461
The palace takes it seriously.

32:03.921 --> 32:05.061
Mother.

32:05.161 --> 32:06.840
Let's think of other solutions,

32:06.841 --> 32:07.981
shall we?

32:15.241 --> 32:17.341
As a woman in the house,

32:18.201 --> 32:20.381
other than being a noble lady,

32:21.081 --> 32:23.141
what advantage do we have?

32:25.001 --> 32:26.781
We can't possibly be like Dou Zhao

32:27.241 --> 32:29.261
to affiliate ourselves
with random hooligans

32:29.441 --> 32:30.941
and their lowly trades.

32:32.361 --> 32:33.501
Ming.

32:37.201 --> 32:38.501
Remember this.

32:38.801 --> 32:40.381
You are a duchess.

32:40.601 --> 32:42.861
Never get involved
in such despicable business.

32:45.521 --> 32:47.181
Keep the money.

32:47.561 --> 32:49.680
Don't be a pushover
in the Duke's residence.

32:49.681 --> 32:51.821
I'll always support you, understood?

32:53.921 --> 32:55.840
Once the Duke has a stable career,

32:55.841 --> 32:58.701
your sister-in-law won't
order you around anymore.

32:59.481 --> 33:00.621
Really?

33:03.001 --> 33:04.341
By then, my worries

33:05.201 --> 33:06.821
will come to an end.

33:08.921 --> 33:10.061
Mother.

33:13.761 --> 33:14.941
Silly girl.

33:21.001 --> 33:22.141
Mind the step.

33:25.161 --> 33:26.301
Go.

33:32.241 --> 33:33.981
Even though you scold her often, Madam,

33:35.121 --> 33:37.141
you love her deeply.

33:38.761 --> 33:40.381
I need to secure a position for the Duke

33:40.561 --> 33:42.661
and arrange everything for her.

33:44.001 --> 33:45.461
Pawn off a few more items

33:45.801 --> 33:47.861
from my personal treasury.

33:48.841 --> 33:49.981
Yes, Madam.

33:52.281 --> 33:54.141
(Yizhi Hall)

33:54.561 --> 33:56.901
(Ledger)
The purchases seem exaggerated.

33:57.261 --> 33:59.880
Check every entry and tell me how much
money has been embezzled.

33:59.881 --> 34:00.611
Madam.

34:00.621 --> 34:03.551
We don't have the matching tokens,
so we can't order the servants around.

34:03.561 --> 34:05.200
They've been rejecting

34:05.201 --> 34:06.681
all our requests.

34:06.821 --> 34:07.920
At this rate,

34:07.921 --> 34:10.201
they're forcing us to pay
from our own pockets.

34:10.211 --> 34:11.911
And that's only one
of our many problems.

34:11.921 --> 34:12.700
What's more,

34:12.701 --> 34:14.340
someone has been spying and listening in

34:14.341 --> 34:17.341
everything you're doing here.

34:17.371 --> 34:19.391
They'd sneak to the Duke's
main residence at night.

34:19.801 --> 34:21.440
I recorded every single one of them.

34:21.441 --> 34:22.570
These servants

34:22.571 --> 34:24.651
are loyal to the Duke of Ying.

34:24.841 --> 34:26.701
In fact, we seem to be

34:26.741 --> 34:28.781
unwelcome in the residence.

34:31.001 --> 34:32.461
What do you think, Lord Song?

34:33.321 --> 34:36.101
Should I replace all our servants
with a new batch?

34:36.991 --> 34:38.861
We cannot control the Duke's servants,

34:38.871 --> 34:41.981
but we can control ours, can't we?

34:42.041 --> 34:43.221
It's not that simple.

34:43.811 --> 34:45.901
All the servants in the Duke's residence

34:46.081 --> 34:47.661
must have had ties to the previous dukes

34:47.751 --> 34:49.541
since generations ago.

34:49.651 --> 34:51.421
Some of them even watched me grow up.

34:51.561 --> 34:53.661
It's not just hard to replace them.

34:53.721 --> 34:55.261
It'll makes me feel bad.

34:55.601 --> 34:57.520
But, we can't let those
servants get their way

34:57.521 --> 34:59.080
and torture our mistress.

34:59.081 --> 35:00.200
Su Lan.

35:00.201 --> 35:01.981
I am married to Lord Song.

35:02.961 --> 35:05.101
Don't see him as an outsider.

35:05.561 --> 35:06.901
I was wrong.

35:06.921 --> 35:08.141
I am sorry, Your Lordship.

35:10.601 --> 35:12.341
Even if we replace our servants now,

35:12.641 --> 35:14.901
it'll take time to gain their loyalty,

35:15.081 --> 35:16.901
and we might attract spies instead.

35:17.201 --> 35:20.381
The Crown Prince and Lord Qing
are trying to win your favor.

35:20.441 --> 35:22.030
If they plant their spies here,

35:22.031 --> 35:23.941
our situation would turn worse.

35:24.001 --> 35:25.621
Your Ladyship, Your Lordship.

35:26.161 --> 35:27.360
We don't have to replace

35:27.361 --> 35:29.221
everyone from the main residence.

35:29.641 --> 35:32.080
They're loyal to the Duke's residence,

35:32.081 --> 35:33.621
not Song Yichun himself.

35:33.961 --> 35:36.461
Your Lordship,
you used to be quite violent,

35:36.641 --> 35:37.840
so they saw you as the enemy

35:37.841 --> 35:40.280
of the Duke's residence.

35:40.281 --> 35:42.821
That's why they're on
Song Yichun's side.

35:43.081 --> 35:44.240
You're right.

35:44.241 --> 35:46.080
If His Lordship

35:46.081 --> 35:48.520
can take control
of the entire residence,

35:48.521 --> 35:52.240
and Her Ladyship obtains
the treasury's matching tokens,

35:52.241 --> 35:53.861
the servants will be on our side.

35:54.361 --> 35:56.221
Now, the key issue

35:56.601 --> 35:57.861
is that Lord Song was beaten up,

35:58.241 --> 36:00.421
and there are signs of foul play
in his mother's death.

36:00.931 --> 36:02.420
Even though we've already replaced

36:02.421 --> 36:03.680
many of our servants,

36:03.681 --> 36:05.101
perhaps some of them

36:05.481 --> 36:07.520
may know the truth behind all these.

36:07.521 --> 36:09.221
That's why we need to keep them here.

36:14.041 --> 36:16.101
Did I say anything wrong, Your Lordship?

36:16.881 --> 36:18.781
You just told Su Lan

36:19.881 --> 36:21.581
not to see me as an outsider,

36:21.881 --> 36:23.261
but what did you just call me?

36:26.801 --> 36:27.941
Yantang.

36:29.801 --> 36:30.941
Say that again.

36:33.201 --> 36:34.381
Yantang.

36:35.841 --> 36:37.080
They're all here.

36:37.081 --> 36:38.000
What are you doing?

36:38.001 --> 36:39.381
- Not anymore.
- Not anymore.

36:44.641 --> 36:46.541
Why are you staring at me like this?

36:47.201 --> 36:49.821
I've always said that
I have a bad reputation.

36:50.241 --> 36:51.381
Now that I think of it,

36:51.521 --> 36:53.621
you used to have an ugly reputation too.

36:53.801 --> 36:55.581
I didn't want to get married back then,

36:56.281 --> 36:58.341
so I didn't care what they
have to say about me.

36:58.881 --> 37:01.541
But, now that we're a married couple,

37:01.641 --> 37:03.040
if you want to advance further,

37:03.041 --> 37:05.080
we can't let Wang Yingxue
and Song Yichun

37:05.081 --> 37:07.501
spread malicious gossip
and damage your reputation.

37:08.631 --> 37:10.341
I need to put an end to this.

37:11.601 --> 37:13.520
I wanted to give you a carefree life,

37:13.521 --> 37:15.280
but now, I'm involving you

37:15.281 --> 37:17.741
in our family affairs.

37:18.121 --> 37:19.301
It's my fault.

37:19.361 --> 37:21.581
My family is no better than yours.

37:21.601 --> 37:23.141
It's no one's fault.

37:23.521 --> 37:26.040
Besides, you said I'm your strategist,

37:26.041 --> 37:27.541
so I have to share your burden.

37:32.041 --> 37:33.661
Strategist, is it?

37:34.121 --> 37:35.781
What's wrong with that?

37:36.241 --> 37:37.581
In fact, you...

37:38.121 --> 37:39.560
What are you doing?

37:39.561 --> 37:41.421
We're discussing serious issues here.

37:42.161 --> 37:44.040
Everything you've been
discussing in this room

37:44.041 --> 37:45.341
isn't serious at all.

37:45.801 --> 37:47.741
Then, what sounds serious to you?

37:49.241 --> 37:50.360
Call me Hubby.

37:50.361 --> 37:51.581
Song Mo.

37:55.901 --> 37:59.020
♪I want to hide like the moon♪

37:59.021 --> 38:02.531
♪Like a butterfly drawn to flowers♪

38:02.761 --> 38:08.880
♪Like ink drops fading into my heart
that turns to longing♪

38:08.881 --> 38:12.660
♪Like the sun waiting
for the flying wild geese♪

38:12.661 --> 38:16.091
♪The sound of weapons
chasing the long whip♪

38:18.201 --> 38:20.360
I was wondering why
His Lordship looked miffed,

38:20.361 --> 38:22.611
and it's because Young Lady
hasn't called him Hubby yet.

38:22.621 --> 38:23.701
I never thought

38:23.721 --> 38:25.621
we would work together
in the same residence.

38:26.441 --> 38:27.920
Just months ago,

38:27.921 --> 38:29.440
we were still enemies.

38:29.441 --> 38:30.861
The future is hard to predict.

38:31.281 --> 38:32.501
I was wondering

38:32.521 --> 38:33.811
what would happen now

38:33.821 --> 38:35.560
if that arrow didn't
miss your vital organs

38:35.561 --> 38:36.701
during the siege.

38:37.081 --> 38:38.120
My friend.

38:38.121 --> 38:40.501
Look, the scar is still here.

38:43.441 --> 38:44.581
Mr. Chen.

38:44.691 --> 38:47.021
We have the best Ganlubai wine here.

38:47.051 --> 38:49.141
Let me offer some to you
to show my apology.

38:49.441 --> 38:50.470
- Sure.
- This way.

38:50.471 --> 38:51.611
This way.

39:03.321 --> 39:05.541
Your Grace, bad news!

39:06.561 --> 39:07.901
Why are you yelling?

39:07.921 --> 39:09.621
Mind your manners.

39:09.881 --> 39:11.981
I think something's wrong.

39:17.401 --> 39:20.061
Everyone in Yizhi Hall
is moving things around.

39:20.361 --> 39:22.680
All those camphor wood chests
are filled with money

39:22.681 --> 39:24.141
to the brim.

39:24.481 --> 39:26.941
There were six or seven people
calculating everything,

39:26.961 --> 39:29.181
so busy until they have
no time to drink water.

39:29.401 --> 39:31.960
Even when we did our year-end
accounts every year,

39:31.961 --> 39:34.861
we'd finish in a day or two.

39:36.961 --> 39:38.861
How much dowry did she bring exactly?

39:39.321 --> 39:42.501
I know the Dous are famous merchants,

39:42.961 --> 39:45.240
but they're not that rich, are they?

39:45.241 --> 39:46.541
Exactly.

39:49.401 --> 39:50.941
Keep an eye on them.

39:50.961 --> 39:53.221
Investigate what's going on.

39:53.401 --> 39:54.541
Yes, Your Grace.

39:57.441 --> 39:59.120
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

39:59.121 --> 40:01.080
If it looks like it's going to rain,

40:01.081 --> 40:02.861
keep the Duke's paintings

40:02.961 --> 40:05.080
so that they don't get wet.

40:05.081 --> 40:06.221
Yes, Your Ladyship.

40:48.441 --> 40:49.581
Well?

40:49.921 --> 40:51.061
Do you like it?

40:51.841 --> 40:52.981
Yes, I do.

40:53.441 --> 40:54.701
I'm glad to see

40:54.961 --> 40:56.141
that you like it.

40:57.961 --> 40:59.901
You were drawing this that day,
weren't you?

41:00.561 --> 41:01.640
That's right.

41:01.641 --> 41:03.901
I wanted to give you a surprise.

41:04.321 --> 41:05.501
It's beautiful.

41:09.201 --> 41:10.341
Your Ladyship.

41:13.401 --> 41:14.360
Your Ladyship.

41:14.361 --> 41:16.471
Madam wants to see you now.

41:17.961 --> 41:19.101
Understood.

41:20.871 --> 41:23.371
Can you come with me?

41:25.241 --> 41:26.381
Ming,

41:26.401 --> 41:27.920
I haven't finished painting today.

41:27.921 --> 41:29.120
- Once I'm done...
- But...

41:29.121 --> 41:30.261
Ming.

41:30.521 --> 41:31.661
Ming, don't worry.

41:31.801 --> 41:33.741
My sister is already married off,

41:33.881 --> 41:35.541
while you're married into this family.

41:37.421 --> 41:38.901
You need to show your prowess

41:38.991 --> 41:40.621
as the mistress of the residence.

41:40.811 --> 41:42.141
Don't let them push you around.

41:52.211 --> 41:53.351
Sister-in-law.

41:54.561 --> 41:55.720
Look at this!

41:55.721 --> 41:57.901
How are you the mistress
of the household?

41:58.241 --> 42:00.120
The residence is heavily in debt now!

42:00.121 --> 42:01.520
What have you been doing?

42:01.521 --> 42:03.080
How unfortunate for us.

42:03.081 --> 42:04.800
If my brother
married your sister instead,

42:04.801 --> 42:07.061
our residence wouldn't be in this state!

42:10.241 --> 42:11.421
Are you mute?

42:13.681 --> 42:15.141
You're right, Sister-in-law.

42:15.761 --> 42:17.821
My mother just gave me
some money last month.

42:18.201 --> 42:19.701
It's only been a while,

42:19.921 --> 42:22.941
and I'm thinking if we could

42:23.041 --> 42:24.160
reduce our spending instead.

42:24.161 --> 42:25.520
Reduce our spending?

42:25.521 --> 42:27.160
This is the Duke's residence!

42:27.161 --> 42:29.240
That's all you can do to keep us afloat?

42:29.241 --> 42:30.600
As the mistress of the residence,

42:30.601 --> 42:32.701
aren't you afraid that people
might laugh at you?

42:33.801 --> 42:36.560
If the residence keeps spending
without any source of income,

42:36.561 --> 42:39.120
we'd eventually go broke
no matter how rich we are.

42:39.121 --> 42:41.920
That's why my mother
begged my grandfather

42:41.921 --> 42:44.240
to appoint the Duke as
the Deputy Commander

42:44.241 --> 42:46.261
of the North Warden's Office.

42:49.921 --> 42:51.061
(Letter of Appointment)

42:53.361 --> 42:55.021
This is his letter of appointment.

42:56.681 --> 42:58.160
I wanted to share this piece of news

42:58.161 --> 43:00.541
together with the Duke and you.

43:06.641 --> 43:08.061
That's more like it.

43:26.921 --> 43:28.240
You're the one

43:28.241 --> 43:30.440
who made Ming lose her child.

43:30.441 --> 43:32.381
If you can't give me
an explanation today,

43:32.401 --> 43:34.570
we'll take this case to court.

43:34.571 --> 43:36.380
Sister, you warned me

43:36.381 --> 43:38.840
that the Duke wouldn't
make a good husband.

43:38.841 --> 43:40.060
Do you regret it?

43:40.061 --> 43:41.260
I'm a beast!

43:41.261 --> 43:43.691
(Request for Divorce)
I was wrong, Ming!

43:46.361 --> 43:49.871
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:50.211 --> 43:53.820
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:53.821 --> 43:59.561
♪Will the pain just
weave itself deeper?♪

44:00.201 --> 44:01.500
♪Where can this
restless heart find peace?♪

44:01.501 --> 44:04.580
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

44:04.581 --> 44:08.441
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

44:08.531 --> 44:12.760
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

44:12.761 --> 44:15.330
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

44:15.331 --> 44:16.580
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

44:16.581 --> 44:19.620
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

44:19.621 --> 44:23.800
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

44:23.801 --> 44:25.780
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

44:25.781 --> 44:28.990
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:28.991 --> 44:35.131
♪Like a stream flowing
steady through time♪

44:37.101 --> 44:44.001
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:44.461 --> 44:51.681
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:51.991 --> 44:55.201
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:55.781 --> 44:59.361
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:59.461 --> 45:05.361
♪Will the pain just
weave itself deeper?♪

45:05.981 --> 45:07.260
♪In this chaotic world♪

45:07.261 --> 45:10.240
♪Only love lasts♪

45:10.241 --> 45:13.991
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

45:14.171 --> 45:18.400
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

45:18.401 --> 45:20.980
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

45:20.981 --> 45:22.180
♪My heart feels empty♪

45:22.181 --> 45:25.110
♪But I can hear your voice♪

45:25.111 --> 45:29.390
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:29.391 --> 45:31.831
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:31.881 --> 45:32.800
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama.)

45:32.801 --> 45:33.680
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:33.681 --> 45:34.680
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home.)

45:34.681 --> 45:40.881
♪Together, we'll make
every moment count♪
